{
  "texts": [
    "This part refers to step 1 in Figure 2.",
    "Inspired by Guo et al. (2023), we designed structured prompts to help LLMs understand the game rules and current state information, including card types, scoring rules, and win/loss conditions.",
    "The game rule template is shown as follows:",
    "• General Rules: A brief game introduction, team position rules, all single cards, and cards ranking.",
    "• Card Type that cannot beat other types: {Description of Card Type 1, Example of Card Type 1}, {Description of Card Type 2, Example of Card Type 2},...; • Card Type that can beat other types: {Description of Card Type 1, Example of Card Type 1}, {Description of Card Type 2, Example of Card Type 2},...; • Single Win/Loss Rule: The scoring rules for four players in a single game, with different combinations of cards being played out in different order."
  ]
}